1
00:00:20,607 --> 00:00:21,537
You okay?

2
00:00:21,647 --> 00:00:24,407
Isn't it amazing, Nishi?

3
00:00:29,587 --> 00:00:31,987
Gramps, I...

4
00:00:32,087 --> 00:00:36,417
Er, what I said back there was...

5
00:00:39,757 --> 00:00:43,097
I'd become a bad person!

6
00:00:43,197 --> 00:00:46,167
I wanted to boast about my evil ways.

7
00:00:46,267 --> 00:00:49,897
I wanted to be known as a tough, rugged man!

8
00:00:50,007 --> 00:00:53,337
I wanted to walk over everybody.

9
00:00:54,907 --> 00:00:56,847
But I wound up here and...

10
00:00:57,347 --> 00:00:59,247
I struggled!

11
00:00:59,347 --> 00:01:02,477
But I managed to survive!

12
