Catch things, walk, see.

14
00:01:10,457 --> 00:01:12,217
Isn't that fun?

15
00:01:12,327 --> 00:01:18,457
Seawater's salty! This place stinks!
But it gives me joy!

16
00:01:18,567 --> 00:01:23,907
Would you rather lie around doing nothing?
Or would you rather feel alive?

17
00:01:24,267 --> 00:01:26,867
