24
00:04:10,767 --> 00:04:13,537
No kidding! Gotta go with the flow, huh?

25
00:04:13,637 --> 00:04:16,267
Yeah, with the flow!

26
00:04:18,947 --> 00:04:20,277
How is it?

27
00:04:23,217 --> 00:04:25,877
Wow! Fantastic!

28
00:04:25,987 --> 00:04:29,287
