Motivation's not gonna get us over that wave.

171
00:19:58,847 --> 00:20:00,567
We need a motor boat!

172
00:20:04,017 --> 00:20:05,637
We've got a motor!

173
00:20:05,887 --> 00:20:07,277
Right here!

174
00:20:10,117 --> 00:20:11,587
But there's no fuel...

175
00:20:12,627 --> 00:20:16,557
Sure there is!
We came here by car, remember?

176
00:20:22,267 --> 00:20:22,927
Yes!

177
00:20:23,037 --> 00:20:23,867
It could work!

178
00:20:23,967 --> 00:20:25,267
It will work!!

179
00:20:29,377 --> 00:20:31,777
We're going to make it!

180
00:20:32,347 --> 00:20:34,277
We're so gonna make it!

181
00:20:35,277 --> 00:20:36,577
Get up there!

182
00:21:36,077 --> 00:21:39,637
The World Cup ends tomorrow
with its final match...

183
00:21:39,747 --> 00:21:42,837
As the world awaits to find out
who'll be the winner...

184
00:21:43,117 --> 00:21:45,107
We're near Osaka again!

185
00:21:45,217 --> 00:21:45,877
Oh, yeah!

186
00:21:45,987 --> 00:21:49,387
I think this is our only chance!

187
00:21:49,587 --> 00:21:54,387
Maybe the whale's come here for us!

188
00:21:54,627 --> 00:21:56,357
And we're going for it!

189
00:22:28,187 --> 00:22:31,187
You're older. Lend it to her!

190
00:22:31,527 --> 00:22:32,827
I don't want to!

191
00:22:32,927 --> 00:22:33,827
Yang.

192
00:22:33,927 --> 00:22:36,827
Don't run like that, Myon'll follow you.

193
00:22:36,937 --> 00:22:38,667
Sorry, Myon...

194
00:22:40,767 --> 00:22:42,797
I don't like that uniform!

195
00:22:43,137 --> 00:22:45,077
- I'll work!
- Sorry Yang!

196
00:22:52,587 --> 00:22:53,637
Wanna try?

197
00:23:01,487 --> 00:23:02,457
Myon.

198
00:23:11,837 --> 00:23:13,167
Yang!

199
00:23:14,007 --> 00:23:15,527
Thanks!

200
00:23:16,607 --> 00:23:19,537
I'm not gonna let you carry
all the load anymore!

201
00:23:19,647 --> 00:23:21,507
I'll grow up.

202
00:23:22,747 --> 00:23:24,177
I'm sorry.

203
00:23:24,277 --> 00:23:28,547
I always knew you were the one
that needed support.

204
00:23:31,557 --> 00:23:35,217
It's your turn, now!

205
00:23:35,597 --> 00:23:38,027
Go ahead!

206
00:24:05,157 --> 00:24:08,127
Here we go kids!

207
00:24:09,697 --> 00:24:12,927
Yes sir!

208
00:25:20,197 --> 00:25:24,157
Run!!

209
00:25:57,097 --> 00:25:58,587
Water striders float...

210
00:25:58,697 --> 00:26:02,697
...using surface tension
from the hairs on their legs.

211
00:26:25,727 --> 00:26:26,457
I'm sorry.

212
00:26:55,827 --> 00:26:58,917
Your bones won't get strong
if you don't drink milk.

213
00:26:59,027 --> 00:27:00,397
Yes, mom!

214
00:27:06,237 --> 00:27:08,757
Ah, not again!

215
00:27:09,407 --> 00:27:11,537
I'll put it in your food then!

216
00:31:05,607 --> 00:31:08,007
This'll be perfect.

217
00:31:09,147 --> 00:31:11,907
- Hey, wrong nail!
- The baby!

218
00:31:12,017 --> 00:31:15,577
- You OK?
- It's heavy!

219
00:31:15,687 --> 00:31:17,017
There!

220
00:31:17,517 --> 00:31:20,617
Mmm, too much space for a little kid!

221
00:31:20,727 --> 00:31:22,717
Ah, he'll be big in no time!

222
00:31:22,997 --> 00:31:25,287
Wonder what he'll be like.

223
00:31:29,797 --> 00:31:32,197
Be right there, sweetie!

224
00:31:32,707 --> 00:31:36,567
Your fever's just gone down you know.

225
00:31:36,677 --> 00:31:37,507
I'm fine.

226
00:31:37,607 --> 00:31:39,367
See you later!

227
00:31:40,107 --> 00:31:41,367
See you at 10!

228
00:31:42,047 --> 00:31:43,637
Keiko? It's me!

229
00:31:44,217 --> 00:31:47,047
Myon? I've got an art show.

230
00:31:47,247 --> 00:31:48,547
That's great!

231
00:31:48,887 --> 00:31:50,477
And she's going for the rope!

232
00:31:50,587 --> 00:31:51,487
"A Lonely Death"

233
00:31:51,587 --> 00:31:53,557
We've got no money either!

234
00:31:54,587 --> 00:31:55,317
Worn by...

235
00:31:59,027 --> 00:31:59,727
There, found it!

236
00:31:59,827 --> 00:32:00,487
Jun!

237
00:32:01,027 --> 00:32:01,997
Hi!

238
00:32:03,167 --> 00:32:04,997
That's insane! They're Yakuzas!!

239
00:32:05,337 --> 00:32:09,737
I told you to wait till tomorrow,
so shut up and wait, you punk!!

240
00:32:10,907 --> 00:32:14,437
Sorry about that! Now back to your interview...

241
00:32:50,747 --> 00:32:51,907
That's her!

242
00:33:17,437 --> 00:33:18,767
Myon!
